<section id="command-setpensize">
    <title>SETPENSIZE</title>
<indexterm><primary>SETPENSIZE</primary></indexterm>

<variablelist>

<varlistentry><term>Synopsis</term>
<listitem>
<synopsis><command>SETPENSIZE</command> <parameter>size</parameter></synopsis>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Description</term>
<listitem>
<para>
Set the pen's thickness.
The <parameter>size</parameter> parameter is a list with two members, width and height.
&PRODUCTNAME; only uses the width member, but this may change.
It is recommended that you set the width and height to the same value.
</para>

</listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>Example</term>
<listitem>

<programlisting><userinput>SETPENSIZE [5 5]
REPEAT 4 [FORWARD 100 RIGHT 90]</userinput></programlisting>

</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>

</section>
